0the%20Play%20store.%20Google%20could%20object%20that%20whatever%20changes%20Epic%20proposes%20are%20too%20sweeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20it%20will%20appeal%20the%20jury's%20verdict.%20It%20could%20also%20appeal%20Donato's%20eventual%20decision%20on%20Epic's%20requested%20remedies%2C%20potentially%20teeing%20up%20years%20of%20additional%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20Epic's%20case%20against%20Apple%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20appeal%20will%20land%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco-based%209th%20U.S.%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20court%20that%20heard%20Epic's%20separate%202020%20antitrust%20case%20against%20Apple%20over%20its%20App%20Store%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appeals%20court%20in%20April%20largely%20ruled%20for%20Apple%2C%20upholding%20a%202021%20decision%20by%20U.S.%20District%20Judge%20Yvonne%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%20that%20said%20Apple's%20app%20rules%20did%20not%20violate%20antitrust%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20scholars%20noted%20that%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20two%20cases%20were%20distinct%2C%20and%20said%20a%20key%20difference%20was%20that%20the%20case%20against%20Apple%20was%20decided%20by%20the%20judge%20directly%2C%20with%20no%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpic's%20bid%20to%20revive%20the%20Apple%20case%20is%20now%20pending%20at%20the%20U.S.%20Supreme%20Court.%20Apple%20also%20appealed%20a%20part%20of%20the%20court's%20order%20that%20would%20require%20it%20to%20make%20some%20changes%20to%20its%20App%20Store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20other%20antitrust%20cases%20is%20Google%20fighting%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20faces%20an%20array%20of%20private%20civil%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20from%20U.S.%20advertisers%20and%20publishers%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20U.S.%20government%20claims%20challenging%20its%20search%20and%20advertising%20technology%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20E.U.%2C%20Google%20is%20trying%20to%20overturn%20a%20%242.6%20billion%20antitrust%20fine%20imposed%20by%20the%20top%20court%20for%20alleged%20market%20abuses%20related%20to%20its%20shopping%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20in%20Epic%20Games'%20case%20does%20not%20directly%20affect%20those%20other%20cases%2C%20but%20it%20could%20spur%20other%20potential%20plaintiffs%20such%20as%20businesses%20and%20app%20developers%20to%20band%20together%20in%20a%20class%20action%2C%20antitrust%20lawyers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20likely%20faces%20a%20jury%20trial%20next%20year%20in%20Virginia%20in%20a%20case%20brought%20by%20the%20U.S.%20Justice%20Department%20and%20a%20group%20of%20states%20over%20its%20dominance%20in%20digital%20advertising.%20Google%20has%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702450740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Frp28o5i_google_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplainer-epic-games-verdict-adds-to-googles-global-antitrust-troubles-4665025%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFortnite%26quot%3B%20maker%20Epic%20Games%20won%20a%20major%20antitrust%20trial%20against%20Alphabets%20Google%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20persuading%20a%20federal%20jury%20on%20Monday%20that%20some%20of%20the%20technology%20giants%20rules%20for%20its%20app%20Play%20store%20violated%20US%20competition%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplainer-epic-games-verdict-adds-to-googles-global-antitrust-troubles-4665025%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplainer-epic-games-verdict-adds-to-googles-global-antitrust-troubles-4665025%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplainer-epic-games-verdict-adds-to-googles-global-antitrust-troubles-4665025%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20Orders%20Protection%20For%20Man%20Allegedly%20Threatened%20By%20BJP%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20Chandigarh%20Police%20to%20provide%20protection%20for%20a%20week%20to%20a%20businessman%20and%20his%20family%20after%20he%20filed%20a%20petition%20alleging%20threats%20from%20BJP%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher%20and%20her%20aide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20filed%20by%20Chaittnya%20Aggarwal%20through%20senior%20advocate%20Anmol%20Rattan%20Sidhu%20submitted%20that%20the%20businessman%2C%20his%20wife%20Ruchika%20Aggarwal%20and%20their%20two%20minor%20daughters%20were%20apprehending%20a%20threat%20to%20their%20lives%20from%20the%20Chandigarh%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20also%20alleged%20that%20there%20were%20some%20financial%20issues%20between%20him%20and%20the%20respondents%20which%20might%20be%20the%20reason%20for%20such%20apprehension.%20He%20submitted%20that%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Kirron%20Kher's%20aide%20Sahdev%20Salaria%20through%20a%20BJP%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20claimed%20that%20Kirron%20Kher%20gave%20him%20Rs%208%20crore%20for%20investment.%20He%20has%20already%20returned%20Rs%202%20crore%20and%20the%20remaining%20is%20to%20be%20returned%2C%20Mr%20Aggarwal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwing%20to%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20market%2C%20the%20petitioner%20sought%20time%20to%20generate%20profits%20on%20the%20investment%20and%20return%20the%20money%2C%20according%20to%20the%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20threatened%20to%20immediately%20return%20the%20money%20along%20with%20interest%20and%20was%20being%20constantly%20harassed%20by%20Ms%20Kher%20and%20her%20aide.%20A%20response%20from%20Kirron%20Kher%20is%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20public%20prosecutor%20Manish%20Bansal%20submitted%20before%20the%20court%20that%20no%20complaint%20has%20been%20received%20in%20any%20police%20station%20regarding%20the%20same%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20petitioner%20or%20his%20wife%20or%20minor%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20submitted%20that%20in%20case%20of%20any%20such%20threat%2C%20there%20is%20helpline%20number%20112%20to%20report%20such%20matters%20but%20neither%20has%20the%20petitioner%20nor%20any%20of%20his%20family%20members%20called%20the%20helpline%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPetitioner's%20counsel%20Sidhu%20submitted%20that%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20the%20profile%20of%20respondent%20no.2%20(Kirron%20Kher)%20if%20they%20have%20straightaway%20come%20to%20this%20court%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20a%20ground%20to%20refuse%20protection%20to%20their%20life%20and%20liberty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20commenting%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case%20and%20the%20admissibility%20value%20of%20any%20of%20the%20allegations%20in%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20court%20said%20in%20a%20December%2011%20order%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20court%20does%20not%20give%20them%20protection%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20that%20might%20amount%20to%20not%20exercising%20the%20constitutional%20jurisdiction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20in%20the%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20peculiar%20to%20this%20case%2C%20it%20shall%20be%20appropriate%20that%20the%20concerned%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20the%20concerned%20SHO%20provide%20appropriate%20protection%20to%20the%20petitioner%20for%20one%20week%20from%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20said%20if%20the%20petitioner%20no%20longer%20required%20the%20protection%2C%20then%20it%20may%20be%20discontinued%20before%20the%20expiry%20of%20the%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20protection%20is%20subject%20to%20the%20stringent%20condition%20that%20from%20the%20time%20such%20protection%20is%20given%2C%20the%20petitioner%20and%20his%20wife%20shall%20not%20go%20outside%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20place%20of%20residence%2C%20except%20for%20medical%20necessities%2C%20to%20buy%20household%20necessities%2C%20and%20for%20bereavements%20in%20the%20families%20of%20the%20close%20relatives%20or%20close%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20imposed%20certain%20restrictions%20to%20ensure%20the%20protection%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Bflaunted%20or%20misutilised%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20clarified%20that%20in%20case%20the%20petitioner%20or%20his%20wife%20violates%20any%20of%20the%20conditions%2C%20the%20order%20of%20protection%20shall%20stand%20recalled%20automatically.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702450440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-08%2Fkirron-kher_650x400_51502114014.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-orders-protection-for-businessman-allegedly-threatened-by-bjp-mp-kirron-kher-4664969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20Chandigarh%20Police%20to%20provide%20protection%20for%20a%20week%20to%20a%20businessman%20and%20his%20family%20after%20he%20filed%20a%20petition%20alleging%20threats%20from%20BJP%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher%20and%20her%20aide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-orders-protection-for-businessman-allegedly-threatened-by-bjp-mp-kirron-kher-4664969%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-orders-protection-for-businessman-allegedly-threatened-by-bjp-mp-kirron-kher-4664969%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-orders-protection-for-businessman-allegedly-threatened-by-bjp-mp-kirron-kher-4664969%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohan%20Yadav%20Takes%20Oath%20As%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20PM%20On%20Stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20of%20two%20BJP%20swearing-ins%20today%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Governor%20Mangubhai%20Patel%20also%20administered%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20to%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Rajendra%20Shukla%20and%20Jagdish%20Devda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElected%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Ujjain%20South%20constituency%20in%20last%20month's%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20previous%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20He%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20belongs%20to%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20which%20make%20up%20over%2048%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2058-year-old%20won%20his%20first%20Assembly%20election%20from%20Ujjain%20South%20in%202013%20and%20was%20re-elected%20in%202018.%20He%20was%20the%20education%20minister%20under%20the%20Chouhan%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav's%20name%20was%20the%20second%20surprise%20pick%20announced%20by%20the%20BJP%20after%20it%20was%20declared%20the%20winner%20in%20three%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20on%20December%203.%20Fighting%20anti-incumbency%20in%20a%20state%20it%20had%20ruled%20for%20nearly%2020%20years%2C%20the%20party%20pulled%20off%20a%20stupendous%20victory%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20winning%20163%20seats%20in%20the%20230-member%20Assembly%20and%20reducing%20the%20Congress%20to%20just%2066.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Mr%20Chouhan%20not%20being%20named%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20pick%20and%20the%20BJP%20banking%20on%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20popularity%20for%20this%20year's%20polls%2C%20experts%20said%20the%20four-time%20chief%20minister's%20popularity%20and%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20especially%20Ladli%20Behna%2C%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20party's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeen%20on%20effecting%20a%20generational%20change%20in%20all%20three%20states%20-%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20-%20however%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20sprang%20a%20surprise%20by%20picking%20Mr%20Yadav%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20had%20moved%20the%20resolution%20proposing%20Mr%20Yadav's%20name%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20was%20present%20at%20the%20swearing-in%2C%20along%20with%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde%20faction)%2C%20Uttarakhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami.%20Union%20Ministers%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20and%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20also%20attended%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPriorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20oath%20ceremony%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20visited%20a%20temple%20in%20Bhopal.%20%26quot%3BI%20belong%20to%20Raja%20Vikramaditya's%20town%20(Ujjain)%20who%20was%20known%20for%20good%20governance.%20The%20oath%20ceremony%20will%20take%20place%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20leader%20-%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20I%20welcome%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20various%20Union%20ministers%20and%20chief%20ministers%20on%20the%20soil%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20priorities%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20focus%20on%20progress%20in%20education%2C%20health%2C%20employment%20(sectors)%20and%20development%20in%20all%20other%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeputies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Shukla%20and%20Jagdish%20Devda%20have%20been%20sworn%20in%20as%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20both%20to%20soothe%20ruffled%20feathers%20and%20to%20balance%20caste%20equations%20ahead%20of%20the%20all-important%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElected%20from%20Malhagarh%20by%20nearly%2060%2C000%20votes%20in%20last%20month's%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Devda%20is%20a%20scheduled%20caste%20leader.%20The%20six-time%20MLA%20was%20first%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20in%201990%20and%20was%20also%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20previous%20Chouhan%20government.%20The%2066-year-old%20held%20the%20post%20of%20Speaker%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Assembly%20for%20a%20few%20months%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shukla%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Rewa%20seat%20for%20a%20fifth%20time%20by%20around%2021%2C000%20votes%2C%20is%20a%20strong%20Brahmin%20face%20of%20the%20party%20from%20the%20Vindhya%20Pradesh%20region%2C%20which%20was%20once%20considered%20a%20Congress%20stronghold.%20The%2059-year-old%20has%20held%20several%20portfolios%2C%20including%20industry%20and%20energy%2C%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702450440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fiiqcab8_mohan-yadav_625x300_13_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohan-yadav-takes-oath-as-madhya-pradesh-chief-minister-pm-on-stage-4664814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20first%20of%20two%20BJP%20swearing-ins%20today%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20