0impact%20player%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRomario%20Shepherd%20has%20been%20in%20the%20IPL%20for%20two%20years%20and%20has%20not%20exactly%20lived%20up%20to%20his%20potential.%20However%2C%20he%20scored%20with%20a%20150%20strike%20rate%20for%20West%20Indies%20against%20England%20and%20picked%20a%20couple%20of%20players%20as%20well.%20Mumbai%20have%20a%20solid%20Indian%20core%20so%20with%20the%20impact%20player%20rule%2C%20Romario%20Shephard%20is%20a%20dangerous%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Shepherd%20has%20played%204%20IPL%20matches%2C%20representing%20LSG%20and%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%20in%20T20I%2C%20Shepherd%20has%20played%2031%20matches%20amassing%20301%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2037.6%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20153.6.%20Coming%20to%20his%20bowling%20statistics%2C%20he%20has%20claimed%2031%20wickets%20with%20an%20economy%20of%2010.38%20his%20best%20bowling%20figure%20remains%20at%204%2F31.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShepherd%20will%20be%20high%20in%20confidence%2C%20having%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20Guyana%20Amazon%20Warriors'%20CPL-winning%20season%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20thrive%20under%20MI's%20new%20bowling%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Lasith%20Malinga%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F639-lasith-malinga-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELasith%20Malinga%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20was%20announced%20as%20the%20bowling%20coach%20for%20the%20franchise%20last%20month.%20Malinga%20will%20fill%20in%20the%20boots%20of%20New%20Zealand%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shane%20Bond%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F129-shane-bond-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShane%20Bond%3C%2Fa%3E%20whose%20successful%20tenure%20lasted%20for%20nine%20years%20with%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702450080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndt