eing%20held%2C%20four%20grueling%20hours%20in%20a%20hotel%20lobby%2C%20waiting%20for%20her%20booking%20to%20be%20confirmed%2C%20culminated%20in%20a%20desperate%20scramble%20for%20a%20ride%20to%20her%208%20am%20practice%20session.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAdventures%20in%20India%20Part%203%20ft%20Nozomi%20Okuhara%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20dont%20think%20after%20such%20experiences%20anyone%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20come%20back%20to%20India%20%2C%20harsh%20reality%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20feel%20sorry%20on%20behalf%20of%20Indian%20Fans%20for%20all%20these%20the%20players%20have%20to%20go%20through%20%F0%9F%99%8F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FluutwyE9dP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FluutwyE9dP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Just%20Badminton%20(%40BadmintonJust)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBadmintonJust%2Fstatus%2F1733855146147557655%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2010%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20reaching%20her%20designated%20hotel%2C%20Ms%20Okuhara%20alleges%20that%20she%20was%20told%20no%20rooms%20were%20available%20for%20immediate%20occupancy.%20A%20representative%20from%20the%20Indian%20Badminton%20Association%20emerged.%20But%20instead%20of%20providing%20much-needed%20assistance%2C%20the%20representative%20allegedly%20surprised%20Okuhara%20with%20an%20unexpected%20and%20bizarre%20request%3A%20a%20selfie.%20The%20Japanese%20badminton%20player%20had%20to%20politely%20turn%20down%20the%20request%20as%20there%20were%20more%20pressing%20matters%20at%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20shuttle%20service%20available%2C%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20kindness%20of%20Indian%20badminton%20stars%20PV%20Sindhu%20and%20HS%20Prannoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20full%20story%20of%20harsh%20travel%20in%20India.%20I%20was%20prepared%20for%20it%2C%20but%20due%20to%20a%20series%20of%20problems%2C%