t%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F28195059%2FScreen-Shot-2020-11-28-at-7.50.21-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20sedition%20for%20a%20newspaper%20column%2C%20which%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20functionary%20complained%20against%20describing%20it%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cobjectionable%E2%80%9D%20piece%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20was%20published%20on%20December%2010%20in%20%3Cem%3ESaamana%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Sena%E2%80%99s%20mouthpiece.%20Based%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Yavatmal%20district%20coordinator%20Nitin%20Bhutada%2C%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20registered%20against%20Raut%2C%20who%20is%20the%20executive%20editor%20of%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaut%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20has%20been%20slapped%20with%C2%A0Sections%20124%20(A)%20(sedition)%2C%20153%20(A)%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence%2C%20language%2C%20etc)%20and%20505%20(2)%20(statements%20creating%20or%20promoting%20enmity%2C%20hatred%20or%20ill-will%20between%20classes)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccensorship%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20had%20no%20right%20to%20say%20that%20it%20stood%20up%20against%20the%20Emergency%20because%20the%20fight%20was%20against%20such%20kind%20of%20censorship.%20The%20criticism%20in%20%3Cem%3ESaamana%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20political%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fsanjay-raut-charged-with-sedition-for-writing-objectionable-article-against-prime-minister-modi%2Farticle67630709.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20maybe%20noted%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20May%2011%20had%20put%20the%20sedition%20law%20in%20abeyance.%20A%20special%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20N.V.%20Ramana%2C%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%2C%20and%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20had%20held%20that%20all%20pending%20cases%2C%20appeals%2C%20and%20proceedings%20concerning%20charges%20framed%20under%20Section%20124A%20should%20be%20kept%20in%20abeyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20said%20in%20August%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Crepealing%E2%80%9D%20the%20sedition%20law%2C%20a%20look%20at%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2Fthe-bharatiya-nyaya-sanhita-2023-485731.pdf%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Section%20150%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eshows%20that%20while%20the%20word%20sedition%20may%20have%20been%20removed%2C%20the%20law%20remains%20and%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20has%20been%20made%20more%20draconian%20by%20making%20it%20punishable%20with%20imprisonment%20for%20life%20or%20seven%20years%20imprisonment%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%202023%20along%20with%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20and%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023%20were%20part%20of%20three%20new%20criminal%20Bills%20introduced%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Creform%E2%80%9D%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20and%20shed%20its%20colonial%20legacy.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%202023%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20replace%20the%20IPC.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20withdrew%20them%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%2012%2C%20following%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702449358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F28195059%2FScreen-Shot-2020-11-28-at-7.50.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsanjay-raut-booked-for-anti-modi-article-under-sedition-law-currently-kept-in-abeyance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20FIR%20was%20booked%20against%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20lodged%20by%20a%20BJP%20functionary%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20former%20had%20written%20an%20'objectionable'%20piece%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20'Saamana'.%20%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsanjay-raut-booked-for-anti-modi-article-under-sedition-law-currently-kept-in-abeyance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Park%20So%20Dam%20overcomes%20Thyroid%20Cancer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702449302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105953779%2Cimgsize-16308.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fpark-so-dam-on-overcoming-thyroid-cancer-challenges-and-finding-strength-to-make-a-comeback-with-deaths-game%2Farticleshow%2F105951656.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105951656.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPark%20So%20Dam%20bravely%20opened%20up%20about%20her%20battle%20with%20papillary%20thyroid%20cancer%20at%20a%20promotional%20press%20conference%20in%20Seoul%20on%20December%2013.%20She%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20the%20support%20she%20received%20during%20her%20recovery.%20Park%20So%20Dam%20discussed%20her%20decision%20to%20return%20to%20acting%20and%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Death%20in%20the%20drama%20'Death's%20Game'.%20Despite%20occasional%20emotional%20challenges%2C%20she%20found%20solace%20and%20strength%20on%20set%2C%20supported%20by%20her%20co-star%20Seo%20In%20Guk.%20'Death's%20Game'%20premieres%20on%20December%2015.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fpark-so-dam-on-overcoming-thyroid-cancer-challenges-and-finding-strength-to-make-a-comeback-with-deaths-game%2Farticleshow%2F105951656.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAb%20Vida%26quot%3B%3A%20Shivraj%20Chouhan's%20%26quot%3BFarewell%26quot%3B%20Ahead%20Of%20Oath%20Ceremony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20before%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20newly%20designated%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20said%20that%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20would%20take%20the%20state%20to%20new%20heights.%20It%20was%20an%20emotional%20moment%20for%20the%20former%20CM%20who%20leaves%20the%20post%20after%20serving%20four%20terms%20as%20he%20bid%20goodbye%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAb%20vida%2C%20jas%20ki%20tas%20rakh%20deni%20chadariya%20(now%20goodbye%20and%20leave%20it%20as%20it%20is).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20made%20the%20remark%20while%20talking%20to%20reporters%20in%20state%20capital%20Bhopal%20ahead%20of%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20at%20Motilal%20Nehru%20Stadium%2C%20Lal%20Parade%20ground%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Bhopal%20on%20Wednesday.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20BJP%20National%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20others%20will%20be%20present%20at%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20has%20also%20said%20that%20he%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20will%20take%20the%20prosperity%2C%20development%20and%20public%20welfare%20in%20the%20state%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state%20will%20take%20oath%20today%20at%2011%3A30%20am%20and%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20he%20(new%20CM)%20will%20take%20the%20prosperity%2C%20development%20and%20public%20welfare%20in%20the%20state%20to%20new%20heights.%20Many%20congratulations%20to%20him.%20Today%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20our%20national%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20are%20arriving%20here.%20I%20welcome%20all%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20took%20stock%20of%20preparations%20for%20the%20oath%20ceremony%20in%20Bhopal%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20his%20duty%20and%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20proper%20arrangements%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bdignified%20ceremony.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20acting%20Chief%20Minister%20right%20now.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20proper%20arrangements%20are%20made%20and%20that%20our%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20take%20oath%20in%20a%20dignified%20ceremony.%20It%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20arrangements%20are%20proper.%20So%2C%20I%20have%20come%20to%20see%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said%20that%20he%20would%20rather%20die%20than%20go%20and%20ask%20something%20for%20himself%20adding%20that%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20will%20achieve%20new%20heights%20under%20the%20CM-designate%20of%20the%20state%20Mohan%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20that%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20the%20BJP%20govt%20will%20complete%20the%20ongoing%20projects%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20terms%20of%20progress%20and%20developme