ot%3B%20Ms%20Kumari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiya%20Kumari%20won%20from%20the%20Vidyadhar%20Nagar%20constituency%20against%20Congress'%20Sitaram%20Agarwal%20with%20a%20margin%20of%2071368%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20the%20granddaughter%20of%20Man%20Singh%20II%2C%20the%20last%20ruling%20maharaja%20of%20the%20princely%20state%20of%20Jaipur.%20Her%20appeal%20for%20votes%20was%20made%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdaughter%20of%20Jaipur%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bprincess%20who%20walks%20on%20the%20streets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20joining%20the%20BJP%20in%202013%2C%20Diya%20Kumari%20has%20won%20the%20two%20elections%20she%20contested.%20She%20became%20an%20elected%20Member%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20Rajasthan%20from%20the%20Sawai%20Madhopur%20constituency%20in%202013.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20she%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Rajsamand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhajan%20Lal%20Sharma's%20name%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Rajasthan%20was%20announced%20by%20BJP's%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20whose%20name%20was%20also%20among%20the%20contenders%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20vote%20count%20painted%20a%20starkly%20different%20picture%20from%20what%20some%20of%20the%20pollsters%20had%20predicted%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20poised%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%20winning%20115%20seats%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20trailing%20at%2069%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702448580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fjdo2ptd_diya-kumari_625x300_11_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-diya-kumari-picked-for-key-rajasthan-role-said-on-vasundhara-raje-4661943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Diya%20Kumari%2C%20who%20ha