2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Holding%20South%20Asia%20Back%20While%20Other%20Asian%20Economies%20Flourish%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13112940%2FScreenshot-2023-12-13-at-11.29.15-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20I%20wrote%20about%20South%20Asia%20remaining%20poor%20compared%20to%20many%20nations%20in%20Asia%2C%20which%20have%20done%20something%20different%20from%20us.%20The%20task%20is%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20wrong%20or%20differently%20and%20what%20is%20undeniably%20different%20about%20us%20and%20them.%20It%20cannot%20only%20be%2C%20as%20is%20argued%2C%20that%20it%20is%20the%20form%20of%20economic%20system%20that%20is%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20tried%20managing%20the%20economy%20through%20central%20planning%20(India%20in%201950s%20and%201960s)%2C%20through%20%E2%80%9Clicence%20raj%E2%80%9D%20(India%20till%20the%201980s)%2C%20through%20%E2%80%9Cliberalisation%E2%80%9D%20(Pakistan%20from%20the%201960s%20and%20India%20from%201991).%20We%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20same%20things%20we%20were%20doing%20before%20(import%20substitution%20in%20India%20in%20the%201970s%20and%20today).%20We%20had%20some%20success%20and%20created%20sectors%20where%20we%20are%20leaders%20(India%20for%20a%20quarter%20century%20or%20so%20in%20information%20technology-enabled%20services%20and%20Bangladesh%20today%20in%20garments).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20cannot%20be%20that%20we%20do%20not%20have%2C%20or%20have%20not%20tried%20to%20have%2C%20hard%20power.%20We%20have%20developed%20nuclear%20weapons%20and%20we%20have%20spent%20large%20sums%20on%20our%20militaries.%20Pakistan%20sends%2017%25%20of%20all%20government%20spending%20to%20the%20Army%2C%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20send%20nine%20per%20cent.%20We%20have%20tried%20to%20be%20strong%20%E2%80%94%20the%20misguided%20word%20used%20here%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmuscular%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20run%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20subcontinent%20with%20the%20military%20(Kashmir%20and%20the%20Northeast%20in%20India%2C%20Balochistan%20in%20Pakistan).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20tried%20to%20remain%20defiant.%20We%20have%20joined%20Western%20alliances%20(Pakistan%20in%201960s)%2C%20we%20have%20remained%20non-aligned%20(India%20in%201950s)%20and%20we%20have%20tried%20a%20patchwork%20of%20things%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20512px)%2085vw%2C%20512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13112349%2FYR0290502_Map-of-South-Asia.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13112349%2FYR0290502_Map-of-South-Asia.jpg%20512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13112349%2FYR0290502_Map-of-South-Asia-300x260.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688964%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22444%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMap%20of%20South%20Asia%2C%201792.%20Credit%3A%20Jan%20Barend%20Elwe%2C%20Public%20Domain%20Dedication%20(CC0%201.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20end%20result%20is%20the%20numbers%20we%20looked%20at%20in%20the%20previous%20column.%20The%20world%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20per%20capita%20per%20year%20is%20an%20average%20of%20%2412%2C262.%20China%20is%20slightly%20ahead%20of%20the%20world%20average%2C%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20one-fifth.%20We%20were%20five%20times%20less%20than%20the%20global%20average%20in%201960%20too%2C%20when%20the%20global%20figure%20was%20at%20%24459%20and%20India%20at%20%2482.%20Note%20that%20this%20is%20per%20person%20income%20and%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%207.7%20billion%20people%2C%20South%20Asia%20contributes%20a%20full%2023%25.%20Meaning%20we%20are%20a%20drag%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economy%20and%20productivity%20and%20have%20been%20for%2060%20years%2C%20at%20more%20or%20less%20the%20same%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20must%20be%20something%20we%20are%20missing.%20What%20is%20it%3F%20The%20World%20Bank%20says%20that%20intra-regional%20trade%20between%20Bangladesh%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20accounts%20for%20five%20percent%20of%20our%20total%20trade%2C%20compared%20to%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20where%20the%20number%20is%20five%20times%20higher.%20Trade%20annually%20here%20is%20%2423%20billion%20though%20it%20should%20really%20be%20over%20%24100%20billion.%20Why%3F%20The%20problem%20is%20purely%20man-made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Bank%20says%20%E2%80%9Cborder%20challenges%20mean%20it%20is%20about%2020%25%20cheaper%20for%20a%20company%20in%20India%20to%20trade%20with%20Brazil%20instead%20of%20a%20neighbouring%20South%20Asian%20country%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20the%20main%20problem%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20broad%20trust%20deficit%20throughout%20the%20region%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20South%20Asia%20is%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20least%20integrated%20regions%20in%20the%20world%20in%20terms%20of%20trade%20and%20people-to-people%20contact.%20Putting%20aside%20traditional%20concerns%20and%20taking%20joint%20action%20can%20develop%20cross-border%20solutions%20to%20shared%20issues%2C%20strengthen%20regional%20institutions%2C%20improve%20infrastructure%20and%20connectivity%2C%20and%20advance%20trade%20policy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20should%20it%20take%20outsiders%20to%20tell%20us%20what%20is%20obvious%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20it%20does.%20The%20World%20Bank%20adds%20that%20regional%20cooperation%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20produce%20significant%20gains%20across%20all%20countries%20of%20South%20Asia%20because%20the%20gap%20in%20trade%20is%20%2444%20billion%20annually.%20We%20have%20the%20space%20to%20reduce%20the%2050%25%20higher%20cost%20for%20container%20shipments%20in%20South%20Asia%20compared%20to%20developed%20nations.%20But%20it%20can%20happen%20only%20if%20we%20are%20less%20hostile%20and%20more%20open%20to%20each%20other%20than%20we%20are%20and%20have%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Ffood-security-south-asian-nations-trade%5C%22%3ETo%20Provide%20Food%20Security%2C%20South%20Asian%20Nations%20Must%20Engage%20in%20Liberal%20Trade%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20one%20thing%20we%20have%20not%20tried.%20We%20have%20not%20opened%20ourselves%20to%20each%20other%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20sort%20of%20geography%20and%20economy%20that%20we%20had%20before%201947.%20Indeed%2C%20we%20have%20not%20devolved%20internally%20power%20from%20the%20Union%20to%20the%20states%20and%20further%20along%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20book%3Cem%3E%20The%2010%20Rules%20of%20Successful%20Nations%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ruchir%20Sharma%20writes%20that%20%E2%80%9Camong%20the%20largest%20emerging%20nations%2C%20trade%20amounts%20to%2060%25%20of%20GDP%20on%20average%2C%20and%20countries%20well%20above%20that%20average%20tend%20to%20be%20major%20export%20manufacturers%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20(142)%2C%20Vietnam%20(210)%2C%20Malaysia%20(131)%2C%20and%20Thailand%20(117)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20something%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20surprise%20us%3A%20%E2%80%9CSouth%20Asia%20remains%20fenced%20off.%20Isolation%2C%20lawlessness%2C%20and%20the%20lingering%20bitterness%20produced%20by%20regional%20wars%20have%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20open%20borders%2C%20and%20so%20far%2C%20no%20leader%20has%20stepped%20forward%20to%20ease%20hostilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20trade%20to%20GDP%20has%20in%20fact%20fallen%20from%2058%25%20of%20GDP%20in%202014%20to%2044%25%20today%2C%20with%20Pakistan%20at%2030%25%20and%20Bangladesh%20at%2028%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20possible%20that%20we%20can%20open%20ourselves%20to%20each%20other%3F%20If%20so%2C%20in%20what%20realistic%20way%2C%20given%20all%20the%20difficulties%20and%20ingrained%20historical%20resistance%3F%20And%20if%20achieved%2C%20what%20are%20the%20effects%20this%20can%20have%20on%20our%20societies%3F%20I%20do%20not%20know%20if%20by%20doing%20this%20we%20can%20repeat%20what%20Taiwan%2C%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%20did%2C%20but%20I%20do%20know%20that%20it%20removes%20the%20one%20restraint%20that%20we%20have%20deliberately%20put%20on%20ourselves%20and%20can%20eliminate%20ourselves.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20not%20even%20discussed%20widely%20today%20in%20the%20region%2C%20despite%20all%20three%20states%20being%20democracies%2C%20tells%20us%20something%20about%20how%20blind%20we%20have%20become%20to%20our%20condition.%20And%20how%20satisfied%20and%20unambitious%20our%20political%20parties%20are%20with%20the%20way%20things%20continue%20to%20remain%20in%20South%20Asia%20as%20we%20enter%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%20Let%20us%20make%20an%20attempt%2C%20however%20modest%2C%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Faakar-patel%5C%22%3EAakar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702448388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13112940%2FScreenshot-2023-12-13-at-11.29.15-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwhat-is-holding-south-asia-back-while-other-asian-economies-flourish%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Increased%20cooperation%20between%20South%20Asian%20countries%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20produce%20significant%20gains%20across%20all%20countries%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwhat-is-holding-south-asia-back-while-other-asian-econo