20the%20new%20state%20government.%20Shukla%20is%20a%20five-time%20MLA%2C%20while%20Devda%20belongs%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20category%20and%20won%20the%202023%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20polls%20from%20the%20Malhargarh%20seat.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20will%20take%20place%20at%2011.30%20am%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20Lal%20Parade%20Ground%20in%20Bhopal.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20BJP-ruled%20states%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20event%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShukla%20is%20a%20strong%20Brahmin%20face%20in%20the%20Vindhya%20Pradesh%20region.%20Here%20are%20five%20facts%20about%20the%20new%20Deputy%20CM%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Born%20on%20August%203%2C%201964%2C%20Shukla%20comes%20from%20an%20engineering%20background.%20He%20held%20the%20president%20post%20of%20the%20student%20union%20at%20the%20Government%20Engineering%20College%20in%201986.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20Shukla%20contested%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20from%20the%20Rewa%20seat%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201998%20but%20lost%20by%20a%20thin%20margin%20of%20over%201%2C000%20votes%20to%20rival%20Independent%20candidate%20Pushpraj%20Singh.%20However%2C%20he%20defeated%20Singh%20in%20the%202003%20state%20elections%20and%20has%20remained%20undefeated%20since.%20This%20election%20year%2C%20he%20won%20the%20seat%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2021%2C339%20votes.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20In%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Shukla%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20Brahmin%20face%20of%20the%20party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Vindhya%20Pradesh%20region%2C%20which%20was%20once%20considered%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%20In%20the%202023%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20defeated%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%2025%20of%20the%2030%20seats%20of%20the%20region.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20Shukla%20has%20held%20several%20ministry%20portfolios%2C%20including%20public%20health%20engineering%2C%20industry%2C%20and%20Energy%20among%20others%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government.%20He%20is%20known%20for%20the%20development%20projects%20he%20carried%20out%20in%20Rewa%2C%20including%20the%20airport%20and%20the%20largest%20solar%20project.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn5.%20He%20is%20married%20to%20Sunita%20Shukla%2C%20and%20they%20have%20three%20children%20-%20two%20daughters%20and%20a%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702447680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fsis25t28_rajendra-shukla-_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-rajendra-shukla-the-new-deputy-cm-of-bjp-led-madhya-pradesh-4664688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajendra%20Shukla%2C%20the%20new%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20Rewa%20Assembly%20seat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-rajendra-shukla-the-new-deputy-cm-of-bjp-led-madhya-pradesh-4664688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-rajendra-shukla-the-new-deputy-cm-of-bjp-led-madhya-pradesh-4664688%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-rajendra-shukla-the-new-deputy-cm-of-bjp-led-madhya-pradesh-4664688%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maratha%20Quota%20Panel%3A%203%20More%20Members%2C%20Chairman%20Quit%20Citing%20Government%20Interference%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13104832%2FGBFx9KUaYAA1RuH.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Three%20more%20members%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Backward%20Class%20Commission%20(MBSCC)%20including%20the%20chairman%2C%20have%20quit%2