0the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Devda%20belongs%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20category.%20He%20contested%20the%202023%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20elections%20from%20the%20Malhargarh%20seat%20and%20won%20by%2059%2C024%20votes.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mr%20Shukla%20is%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20Rewa%20Assembly%20seat%20and%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20Brahmin%20face%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20Vindhya%20Pradesh%20region.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20five%20key%20facts%20about%20Jagdish%20Devda%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Born%20in%20Rampura%20village%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Neemuch%20district%2C%20Jagdish%20Devda%20is%20a%20six-time%20MLA%20and%20was%20first%20elected%20to%20the%20state%20Assembly%20in%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20He%20held%20the%20office%20of%20Ministry%20Of%20Finance%20in%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan-led%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Trained%20to%20be%20a%20lawyer%2C%20the%2066-year-old%20began%20his%20political%20career%20with%20the%20BJP%20Yuva%20Morcha%20BJP's%20youth%20wing%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0Bharatiya%20Janata%20Yuva%20Morcha%20(BJYM)%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0in%201979.%20He%20held%20several%20posts%2C%20including%20mandal%20president%2C%20district%20general%20secretary%2C%20and%20district%20president%20in%20the%20Mandsaur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Mr%20Devda%20even%20served%20as%20the%20student%20union%20president%20at%20the%20Government%20College%2C%20Rampura.%20Known%20for%20his%20organisational%20skills%2C%20Mr%20Devda%20has%20held%20several%20ranks%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20In%202003%2C%20he%20also%20held%20the%20home%2C%20school%20education%2C%20and%20energy%20portfolios%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20state.%20Mr%20Devda%20was%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20for%20a%20short%20period%20from%20March%2024%20to%20July%202%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3