es.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshabana-azmi-to-feature-in-chef-vikas-khannas-next-film-deets-inside%2Farticleshow%2F105952331.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105952331.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERenowned%20chef%20and%20filmmaker%20Vikas%20Khanna%2C%20known%20for%20his%20global%20culinary%20expertise%2C%20is%20set%20to%20direct%20his%20fourth%20film%20based%20on%20his%20book%20%26quot%3BFlavors%20First.%26quot%3B%20The%20lead%20role%20will%20be%20played%20by%20acting%20powerhouse%20Shabana%20Azmi.%20Khanna%20expresses%20excitement%20about%20the%20project%2C%20aiming%20to%20bring%20a%20new%20dimension%20to%20his%20culinary%20and%20filmmaking%20skills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshabana-azmi-to-feature-in-chef-vikas-khannas-next-film-deets-inside%2Farticleshow%2F105952331.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Votes%20For%20UN%20Ceasefire%20Resolution%2C%20Israel%20Faces%20Pressure%20From%20Allies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFacing%20calls%20from%20many%20members%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20is%20now%20coming%20under%20pressure%20from%20its%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20has%20criticised%20its%20bombing%20in%20the%20small%20strip%20of%20land%20as%20%26quot%3Bindiscriminate%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20among%20the%20countries%20that%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%2C%20'Protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20upholding%20legal%20and%20humanitarian%20obligations'%2C%20demanding%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.%20As%20many%20as%20153%20countries%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20resolution%2C%20while%2010%2C%20including%20US%2C%20Israel%20and%20Austria%2C%20voted%20against%20it%20and%2023%2C%20including%20Germany%2C%20Argentina%20and%20Ukraine%20abstained%20from%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%20Hamas%20operatives%20launched%20a%20massive%2C%20multi-pronged%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20which%20has%20been%20described%20as%20the%20bloodiest%20in%20the%20country's%20history.%20Around%201%2C200%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20around%20240%20people%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20were%20Israelis%2C%20were%20taken%20hostage.%20After%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20launched%20a%20withering%20offensive%20on%20Gaza%2C%20vowing%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20bring%20the%20hostages%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20hostages%20had%20been%20freed%20as%20part%20of%20a%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20last%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%2C%20the%20war%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2018%2C400%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%20that%20at%20least%20another%2050%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20latest%20wave%20of%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20across%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20AFP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Starting%20To%20Lose%20Support'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20most%20blunt%20remarks%20since%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20US%20President%20Biden%20told%20a%20campaign%20event%20in%20Washington%20that%20Israel%20had%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20the%20world%20supporting%20it%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they're%20starting%20to%20lose%20that%20support%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20bombing%20that%20takes%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AFP%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20news%20conference%20later%2C%20Mr%20Biden%20toned%20down%20his%20comments%20and%20reiterated%20his%20country's%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20but%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20safety%20of%20innocent%20Palestinians%20is%20still%20of%20great%20concern%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Biden's%20remarks%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Washington's%20repeated%20calls%20to%20Israel%20to%20take%20more%20care%20to%20avoid%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20Gaza%2C%20saying%20too%20many%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20also%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisagreement%26quot%3B%20with%20Biden%20over%20how%20a%20post-conflict%20Gaza%20would%20be%20governed%2C%20reflecting%20a%20rare%20rift%20between%20the%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Continuous%20Suffering'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Israeli%20allies%2C%20Australia%2C%20Canada%20and%20New%20Zealand%20issued%20a%20joint%20statement%20and%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20saying%20that%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%20must%20be%20protected%20and%20that%20Israel%20must%20respect%20International%20humanitarian%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognise%20Israel's%20right%20to%20exist%20and%20right%20to%20defend%20itself.%20In%20defending%20itself%2C%20Israel%20must%20respect%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%20Civilians%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%20must%20be%20protected.%20We%20are%20alarmed%20at%20the%20diminishing%20safe%20space%20for%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20price%20of%20defeating%20Hamas%20cannot%20be%20the%20continuous%20suffering%20of%20all%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Ministers%20Anthony%20Albanese%2C%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20Christopher%20Luxon%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20deeply%20concerned%20by%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%20and%20ongoing%20risks%20to%20all%20Palestinian%20civilians.%20Safe%20and%20unimpeded%20humanitarian%20access%20must%20be%20increased%20and%20sustained%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20joint%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20statement%20came%20after%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly's%20resolution%2C%20with%20the%20number%20of%20countries%20that%20voted%20for%20it%20exceeding%20the%20140%20or%20so%20that%20have%20routinely%20backed%20resolutions%20condemning%20Russia%20for%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Hell%20On%20Earth'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner-General%20of%20the%20UN%20agency%20for%20Palestinian%20refugees%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%20described%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20as%20%26quot%3Bhell%20on%20earth%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20in%20%23Gaza%2C%20endless%20deepening%20tragedy.%20People%20are%20everywhere%2C%20live%20in%20the%20street%2C%20need%20everything.%20They%20plead%20for%20safety%20%26amp%3B%20for%20an%20end%20to%20this%20hell%20on%20earth%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lazzarini%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaw%20videos%20of%20an%20%40UNRWA%20%C2%A0school%20in%20northern%20%23Gaza%20blown%20up.%20It%20is%20outrageous.%20All%20public%20facilities%2C%20including%20hospitals%20%26amp%3B%20%40UN%20schools%20are%20protected%20under%20international%20law.%20Parties%20to%20this%20brutal%20war%20have%20the%20coordinates%20of%20all%20our%20facilities%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20another%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%20City%2C%20Hamas%20said%20via%20Telegram%20that%20Israeli%20forces%20raided%20a%20hospital%20and%20detained%20its%20director%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AFP%20report%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20did%20not%20immediately%20comment%2C%20but%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20Hamas%20of%20using%20hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20mosques%20and%20tunnels%20beneath%20them%20as%20military%20bases.%20Hamas%20has%20denied%20these%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%20said%20on%20X%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20worried%26quot%3B%20by%20reports%20of%20the%20raid%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20agency%20%26quot%3Burgently%20calls%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20all%20persons%20inside%20the%20hospital%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20the%20UN%20humanitarian%20agency%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20had%20said%20fighting%20had%20been%20reported%20near%20the%20hospital%20for%20three%20consecutive%20days.%20It%20also%20said%20two%20mothers%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20strike%20on%20the%20maternity%20ward%2C%20and%20that%20about%203%2C000%20displaced%20people%20were%20trapped%20in%20the%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20air%20and%20ground%20campaign%20has%20reduced%20much%20of%20Gaza%20to%20rubble.%20The%20United%20Nations%20said%20its%20satellite%20analysis%20agency%20UNOSAT%20had%20determined%2C%20based%20on%20a%20November%2026%20image%2C%20that%2018%20per%20cent%20of%20Gaza's%20infrastructure%20had%20been%20destroyed%2C%20the%20AFP%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChildren%20Displaced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20also%20estimates%201.9%20million%20of%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20by%20the%20conflict%2C%20half%20of%20them%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAid%20groups%20have%20warned%20the%20territory%20will%20soon%20be%20overwhelmed%20by%20starvation%20and%20disease%2C%20and%20are%20pleading%20with%20Israel%20to%20boost%20efforts%20to%20protect%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20spread%20of%20diseases%20in%20Gaza%20has%20reportedly%20intensified%2C%20especially%20due%20to%20overcrowded%20living%20conditions%3B%20which%20adds%20to%20the%20strain%20on%20an%20increasingly%20overwhelmed%20health%20system%20and%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20people%20dying%2C%26quot%3B%20OCHA%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20killed%20at%20least%2024%20people%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Rafah%2C%20where%20tens%20of%20thousands%20are%20seeking%20shelter%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Rafah%20hospital%2C%20bereaved%20father%20Hani%20Abu%20Jamaa%20cradled%20the%20body%20of%20his%20young%20daughter%20Sidal%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20by%20shrapnel%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AFP%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20had%20been%20strong%20explosions%20overnight%20and%20he%20only%20found%20she%20was%20dead%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20wake%20her%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20I%20live%20100%20years%2C%20I%20will%20never%20find%20another%20like%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20crying.%20%26quot%3BMay%20God%20have%20mercy%20on%20her%2C%20oh%20Lord.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFears%20of%20a%20wider%20conflict%20continue%20to%20grow%2C%20with%20Iran-backed%20groups%20targeting%20US%20and%20allied%20forces%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%2C%20and%20daily%20exchanges%20of%20fire%20along%20Israel's%20border%20with%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20in%20response%20to%20projectiles%20fired%20Tuesday%20from%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria%2C%20it%20retaliated%20by%20striking%20launch%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702446180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fq85i0t2_gaza_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-votes-for-un-ceasefire-resolution-israel-faces-pressure-from-allies-4664722%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Facing%20calls%20from%20many%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20is%20now%20coming%20under%20pressure%20from%20its%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20which%20has%20criticised%20its%20bombing%20in%20the%20small%2