05950968.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhighest-grossing-films-of-2023%2Fphotostory%2F105950968.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahadev%20App%20Promoter%20Detained%20In%20Dubai%2C%20May%20Be%20Deported%20To%20India%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20development%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20main%20promoters%2C%20Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20has%20been%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20in%20Dubai%20based%20on%20a%20red%20corner%20notice%20issued%20by%20Interpol%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20Uppal%20was%20detained%20last%20week%20and%20sources%20said%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20deported%20to%20India%20soon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahadev%20app%2C%20which%20reportedly%20turned%20over%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore%20a%20day%2C%20had%20also%20caused%20a%20political%20stir%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20in%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20claimed%20that%20a%20cash%20courier%2C%20Asim%20Das%2C%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20promoters%20of%20the%20app%20had%20paid%20Rs%20508%20crore%20to%20then%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%20When%20he%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20court%2C%20however%2C%20the%20courier%20had%20said%20he%20was%20being%20framed%20as%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20and%20he%20had%20never%20delivered%20any%20cash%20to%20politicians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20investigation%2C%20the%20agency%20found%20that%20Uppal%20holds%20a%20passport%20of%20Vanuatu%2C%20a%20country%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20and%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Broaming%20freely%26quot%3B%20using%20that%2C%20but%20had%20not%20given%20up%20his%20Indian%20citizenship.%20He%20had%20also%20applied%20for%20an%20Australian%20visa%20using%20the%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20promoter%20of%20the%20app%2C%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%2C%20whose%20Rs%20200-crore%20wedding%20in%20Dubai%20had%20been%20attended%20by%20several%20Bollywood%20celebrities%20in%20February%2C%20is%20still%20on%20the%20run%20and%20efforts%20are%20on%20to%20trace%20him%2C%20ED%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20App%20Worked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED%20investigation%20so%20far%2C%20the%20key%20movers%20behind%20the%20app%20were%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal%2C%20who%20hailed%20from%20Bhilai%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20but%20operated%20out%20of%20Dubai.%20Several%20subsidiary%20betting%20apps%20were%20run%20by%20the%20two%20men%20and%20several%20other%20people%2C%20and%20call%20centres%20were%20operated%20in%20different%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Thailand%20and%20the%20UAE.%20At%20least%2030%20call%20centres%20were%20run%20over%20India%2C%20including%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apps%20run%20by%20this%20organisation%20witnessed%20transactions%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20and%20their%20daily%20profit%20was%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20nearly%20Rs%20200%20crore%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EED%20officials%20said%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal%20also%20had%20links%20with%20the%20police%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20politicians%2C%20and%20regular%20payments%20were%20made%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20app%20stayed%20off%20the%20radar%20of%20investigating%20agencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20arrested%206%20people%20in%20the%20case%20-%20Sunil%20Damani%2C%20Anil%20Damani%2C%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%20Chandrabhushan%20Verma%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Police%2C%20a%20constable%20and%20Satish%20Chandrakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoles%2C%20Linkages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20operations%20were%20being%20run%20by%20brothers%20Anil%20and%20Sunil%20Damani%2C%20who%20were%20close%20associates%20of%20the%20promoters.%20ED%20officials%20said%20the%20Damani%20brothers%20opened%20several%20benami%20bank%20accounts%2C%20which%20were%20used%20to%20move%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promoters%20would%20send%20cash%20to%20the%20Damani%20brothers%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20using%20hawala%20channels%20and%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%20Chandrabhushan%20Verma%20would%20deliver%20part%20of%20it%20to%20police%20officers%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20politicians%20as%20bribes%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20interrogation%2C%20Anil%20Damani%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20and%20his%20brother%20had%20done%20transactions%20worth%20Rs%2060%20to%2065%20crore%20through%20hawala%20channels%20in%20the%20past%20two-three%20years%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Uppal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnil%20Damani%20also%20said%20that%20the%20brothers%20ran%20a%20hawala%20channel%20through%20their%20jewellery%20shop%20in%20Raipur.%20Their%20call%20details%20have%20revealed%20that%20they%20were%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20Uppal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatish%20Chandrakar%20ran%20four%20call%20centres%20for%20the%20organisation%20and%20had%20a%20five%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20them.%20He%20also%20looked%20after%20illegal%20money%20transactions%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20links%20with%20known%20gangster%20and%20drug%20dealer%20Tapan%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20Uppal%20and%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%20have%20denied%20their%20involvement%20with%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20or%20the%20betting%20syndicate%20and%20said%20that%20these%20were%20run%20by%20one%20Shubham%20Soni%2C%20who%20is%20also%20based%20in%20Dubai.%20The%20courier%20who%20was%20caught%20with%20over%20Rs%205%20crore%20ahead%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20elections%20had%20claimed%20he%20had%20been%20giv