t%20is%20the%20brand%20of%20cricket%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20play.%20The%20message%20was%20loud%20and%20clear.%20Irrespective%20of%20what%20the%20situation%20is%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20enjoy%20yourself%2C%20and%20we%20will%20see%20what%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Suryakumar%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tough.%20I%20told%20the%20boys%20that%20we%20are%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20comfort%20zone%2C%20we%20have%20to%20something%20different.%20This%20situation%20can%20come%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20batted%20beautifully%20in%20the%20first%205-6%20overs%20and%20took%20the%20game%20away%20from%20us.%20It%20was%20the%20brand%20of%20cricket%20we%20were%20talking%20about%2C%20just%20go%20out%20and%20express%20ourselves.%20It%20was%20tough%20with%20the%20wet%20ball%2C%20but%20we%20would%20face%20similar%20situations%20in%20the%20future%20and%20it's%20a%20good%20learning%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa's%20batting%20order%20was%20in%20control%20from%20the%20first%20ball%2C%20with%20India%20making%20some%20inroads%20in%20the%20middle%20order%2C%20but%20Andile%20Phehlukwayo%20smashed%20the%20winning%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHendricks'%20knock%20of%2049%20and%20Tristan%20Stubbs'%20unbeaten%20cameo%20of%2014%20runs%20followed%20by%20Gerald%20Coetzee's%20three-wicket%20haul%20powered%20South%20Africa%20to%20a%20five-wicket%20victory%20over%20India%20via%20the%20DLS%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20India%20in%20the%20first%20inning%2C%20Suryakumar%20and%20Rinku%20Singh%20starred%20with%20the%20bat%20as%20they%20slammed%2056%20and%2068%20respectively%20guiding%20their%20team's%20total%20to%20180%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20final%20T20I%20between%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20will%20be%20played%20at%20the%20New%20Wande