EPenn%20President%20Liz%20Magill%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E's%20resignation%2C%20following%20months%20of%20criticism%20and%20a%20botched%20congressional%20testimony%2C%20rocked%20academia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20celebrated%20it%20as%20a%20win%20against%20antisemitism%3B%20others%20viewed%20it%20as%20curbing%20free%20speech%20and%20the%20right%20to%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20many%20reasons%20Magill%20stepped%20down%2C%20one%20possible%20factor%20is%20straightforward%3A%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20responsibilities%20of%20a%20modern%20college%20professor%20are%20two-fold%2C%20Michael%20Hemesath%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20Carleton%20College%20and%20the%20former%20president%20of%20Saint%20John's%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20over%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternally%2C%20their%20job%20is%20to%20focus%20the%20school's%20academic%20mission%20and%20campus%20culture.%20Externally%2C%20they%20must%20serve%20as%20the%20school's%20public%20face%20and%20fundraise%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20is%20taking%20up%20more%20time%20as%20private%20donations%20become%20integral%20to%20universities'%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20decades%2C%20the%20role%20of%20a%20university%20president%2C%20particularly%20at%20bigger%20institutions%2C%20has%20shifted%20significantly%20toward%20more%20external%20commitments%2C%20primarily%20fundraising%20as%20institutions%20grow%20more%20complex%20and%20educational%20costs%20have%20continued%20to%20rise%20faster%20than%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Hemesath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20big%20research%20institution%2C%20external%20responsibilities%20can%20take%20up%2075%25%20or%20more%20of%20a%20president's%20time%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2060%25%20of%20respondents%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acenet.edu%2FDocuments%2FAmerican-College-President-VIII-2017.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2017%20American%20College%20Presidents%20Study