no%20wool.%20What%20really%20seals%20the%20deal%20in%20terms%20of%20wearability%20is%20the%20expertly%20designed%2C%20hidden%20Oxford%20buttondown%20collar%20%E2%80%93%20that%20makes%20this%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performance%20dress%20shirts%20you%20can%20actually%20wear%20with%20dark%20blue%20jeans%20as%20well%20as%20tailored%20wool%20trousers%20or%20stretch%20cargo%20chinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20business%20casual%3Cp%3EOpt%20for%20a%20better%20kind%20of%20business%20casual%20by%20switching%20out%20your%20polo%20for%20a%20stretchy%20dress%20shirt%20in%20an%20eye-catching%20color.%20B.%20Draddy%20specializes%20in%20performance%20apparel%20suitable%20for%20the%20golf%20course%2C%20but%20this%20cotton-nylon%20stretch%20shirt%20is%20well-suited%20for%20a%20post-links%20dinner%20or%20drinks%20(and%20again%2C%20the%20office).%20Memory%20collar%20stays%20ensure%20your%20collar%20frames%20your%20face%2C%20rather%20than%20lays%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20business%20formal%3Cp%3EFor%20formal%20affairs%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20from%20a%20black%20tie%20to%20an%20all-important%20business%20meeting%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dress%20shirt%20with%20a%20more%20dressy%20flair%20is%20more%20than%20acceptable.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20practically%20required%2C%20and%20Eton%20dress%20shirts%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion.%20The%20elastane-enhanced%20recycled%20yarn%20is%20plenty%20stretchy%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20cutaway%20collar%20that%20takes%20this%20performance-minded%20shirt%20to%20the%20next%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20with%20pockets%3Cp%3ESome%20dress%20shirts%20are%20made%20for%20only%20the%20most%20buttoned-up%20offices%2C%20but%20others%20inject%20a%20touch%20of%20outdoor-ready%20performance%20into%20the%20mix.%20KUHL%20used%20an%20advanced%20polyester%20performance%20fabric%20featuring%20UPF%2B%20technology%20to%20nail%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20rugged%20and%20refined.%20Better%20still%20is%20the%20handy%20pocket%20to%20store%20small%20EDC%20essentials%20when%20the%20time%20comes%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20made-to-measure%3Cp%3EBuying%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performance%20dress%20shirts%20doesn't%20have%20to%20feel%20intimidating%20%E2%80%93%20it%20can%20be%20as%20easy%20as%20taking%20your%20measurements%20(a%20fairly%20simple%20process)%20and%20then%20selecting%20from%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20options%20via%20Woodies.%20The%20results%20are%20tailored%20to%20your%20liking%2C%20from%20the%20collar%20to%20the%20cuff%20design%2C%20and%20you%20can%20even%20add%20a%20monogram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fperformance-dress-shirts%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702417206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646651dffb9a9d0018c914cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fperformance-dress-shirts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wrinkle-free%20dress%20shirts%20made%20of%20breathable%20materials%20offer%20style%20and%20comfort.%20We've%20rounded%20up%20the%20best%20performance%20dress%20shirts%20for%20men.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22beauhayhoe%40gmail.com%20(Beau%20Hayhoe)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fperformance-dress-shirts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22USWNT%20players%20get%20real%20about%20what%20went%20wrong%20at%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20in%20Netflix's%20new%20doc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Women's%20National%20Team%20players%20react%20after%20losing%20their%202023%20World%20Cup%20Round%20of%2016%20soccer%20match%20against%20Sweden%20in%20a%20penalty%20shootout.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657