mbassador%20to%20India%2C%20Eric%20Garcetti%2C%20publicly%20acknowledged%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnarendra-modi-joe-biden-invited-chief-guest-2024-republic-day-parade%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20extended%20an%20invitation%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20the%20US%20President%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20guest%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20in%20January%202024.%20While%20Garcetti%20didn%E2%80%99t%20publicly%20link%20it%20to%20the%20Quad%20summit%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20external%20affairs%20minister%20himself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37283%2FTranscript%2Bof%2BPress%2BBriefing%2Bon%2Bthe%2BIndiaAustralia%2BForeign%2BMinisters%2BFramework%2BDialogue%2BNovember%2B21%2B2023%5C%22%3Econfirmed%20in%20Novembe%3C%2Fa%3Er%20that%20India%20would%20host%20a%20leaders%E2%80%99%20meeting%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20next%20year%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20a%20month%20left%2C%20Indian%20official%20sources%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Quad%20summit%20is%20%E2%80%9Cproposed%20to%20be%20held%20later%20in%202024%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20looking%20for%20revised%20dates%20as%20the%20dates%20currently%20under%20consideration%20do%20not%20work%20with%20all%20the%20Quad%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20does%20not%20address%20the%20invitation%20to%20Biden%2C%20but%20it%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20the%20US%20President%20would%20be%20considering%20two%20separate%20visits%20to%20India%20in%20one%20year.%20He%20was%20already%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20September%20for%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20embassy%20has%20not%20issued%20any%20separate%20announcement%20on%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20Indian%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20serious%20allegations%20by%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20a%20fortnight%20that%20an%20%E2%80%9Cidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%E2%80%9D%20had%20directed%20the%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20a%20US%20citizen%20on%20American%20soil%2C%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20continued.%20Even%20before%20the%20charges%20were%20filed%2C%20when%20the%20US%20government%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20alleged%20plot%20to%20kill%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20engagements%20between%20Washington%20and%20New%20Delhi%20took%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3Ebusiness-as-usual%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20Indian%20agents%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Khalistan%20activist%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20in%20June.%20After%20this%20claim%2C%20at%20least%20some%20evidence%20for%20which%20was%20provided%20by%20the%20US%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20Pannun%20%E2%80%98plot%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20US%20secretary%20of%20state%20and%20defence%20secretary%20travelled%20to%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-two-months-india-transitioned-from-aspiring-global-south-leader-to-plain-us-ally%5C%22%3Efor%20a%202%2B2%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Australia%20also%20celebrating%20its%20National%20Day%20on%20January%2026%2C%20it%20had%20been%20a%20non-starter%20to%20consider%20all%20the%20quad%20leaders%20as%20chief%20guests%20for%20Republic%20Day.%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20also%20had%20some%20scheduling%20conflicts%20due%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Biden%20was%20invited%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%2C%20the%20intention%20was%20for%20the%20leaders%20from%20Japan%20and%20Australia%20to%20join%20him%20for%20the%20leaders%E2%80%99%20summit%20on%20January%2027.%20However%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20invitations%20to%20US%20presidents%20to%20be%20chief%20guests%20at%20Republic%20Day%20functions%20have%20always%20clashed%20with%20the%20annual%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20delivered%20by%20the%20US%20president%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20calendar%20year%20to%20a%20joint%20session%20of%20the%20US%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Barack%20Obama%20was%20the%20only%20US%20president%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20Day%20parade.%20With%20the%20invitation%20sent%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20Modi%20becoming%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20Obama%20administration%20went%20an%20extra%20step%20to%20work%20with%20the%20US%20Congress%20to%20ensure%20that%20preparations%20for%20the%20annual%20address%20did%20not%20impact%20the%20presidential%20visit.%20He%20delivered%20the%20address%20on%20January%2020%2C%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20with%20Biden%20declining%20India%E2%80%99s%20invite%20this%20time%20around%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20second%20time%20that%20the%20US%20has%20turned%20down%20an%20invitation%20for%20the%20President%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20guest.%20India%20had%20previously%20invited%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20guest%20for%20the%202019%20Republic%20Day%20parade.%20However%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dtrump%2Bturns%2Bdown%2Binvite%2Bthewire.in%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3ETrump%20administration%20had%20turned%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20invite%20citing%20domestic%20commitments%2C%20especially%20the%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20time%2C%20Washington%20expressed%20its%20regret%20to%20India%20over%20Trump%20not%20being%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%2C%20prompting%20India%C2%A0to%20arrange%20for%20another%20world%20leader%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20guest.%20In%202019%2C%20South%20African%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%20took%20on%20the%20mantle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinding%20time%20for%20the%20Quad%20summit%20later%20in%202024%20will%20also%20be%20tricky%20as%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20campaign%20will%20be%20in%20full%20swing.%20The%20US%20will%20have%20its%20presidential%20elections%20in%20early%20November%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20about%20six%20weeks%20left%20for%20Republic%20Day%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20who%20will%20step%20forward%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20national%20celebrations%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20go%20into%20campaign%20mode%20with%20general%20elections%20set%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April-May%20next%20year.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20Quad%20summit%20has%20now%20been%20postponed%20for%20the%20latter%20half%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702384607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F24142027%2FFw2JZ3vWIAE8DoU.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbiden-wont-be-the-republic-day-chief-guest-scheduled-quad-summit-in-january-postponed-officials%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20official%20sources%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Quad%20summit%20is%20'proposed%20to%20be%20held%20later%20in%202024'.%20The%20statement%20does%20not%20address%20the%20invitation%20to%20Biden%2C%20but%20it%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20the%20US%20President%20would%20be%20considering%20two%20separate%20visits%20to%20India%20in%20one%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbiden-wont-be-the-republic-day-chief-guest-scheduled-quad-summit-in-january-postponed-officials%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%3A%20First-Time%20MLA%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20Is%20New%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12175218%2FGBDRaWFW8AAmpdq.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20BJP%20has%20announced%20that%20first-time%20MLA%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20will%20be%20the%20next%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20while%20Diya%20Kumari%20and%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20will%20be%20his%20deputies.%20The%20Ajmer%20North%20MLA%20Vasudev%20Devnani%20will%20be%20the%20assembly%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%2C%20the%2056-year-old%20MLA%20from%20Sanganer%2C%20is%20a%20long-time%20party%20member%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20ABVP%20during%20his%20student%20days.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-is-bjps-rajasthan-chief-minister-choice-4659836%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20general%20secretary%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20organisation%20man.%20Sharma%20has%20an%20MA%20in%20politics%20from%20Rajasthan%20University%20and%20has%20declared%20one%20criminal%20case%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20announcement%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20now%20dropped%20all%20of%20its%20previous%20chief%20ministers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan)%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20(Raman%20Singh)%20and%20Rajasthan%20(Vasundhara%20Raje).%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-yadav-little-known-outside-ujjan-bjps-cm-pick-for-mp-baffles-party-leaders-cadres%5C%22%3EMohan%20Yadav%20was%20chosen%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-bjp-ends-week-long-suspense-names-vishnu-deo-sai-as-next-chief-minister%5C%22%3EVishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20will%20lead%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%20asked%20Raje%20to%20propose%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20name%20as%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20at%20the%20legislature%20party%20meeting%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon.%20The%20central%20observers%20for%20the%20meeting%20were%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Vinod%20Tawde%20and%20Saroj%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202003%20elections%2C%20Sharma%20contested%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%20from%20the%20Nadbai%20constituency%20but%20secured%20only%205%2C969%20votes%20out%20of%20the%20total%2095%2C018%20valid%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20five%20terms%2C%20either%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20or%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20have%20been%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20a%20convincing%20victory%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20bagging%20115%20of%20the%20199%20seats%20that%20went%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20a%20September%20rally%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20declared%20that%20the%20party%20would%20not%20project%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20face.%20However%2C%20leaders%20like%20Rajyavardhan%20Rathore%2C%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20Kirodilal%20Meena%2C%20and%20Baba%20Balaknath%20were%20among%20those%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20contenders%20for%20the%20position%20included%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leader%20of%20opposition%20Rajendra%20Rathore%2C%20and%20Jat%20Leader%20Satish%20Poonia.%20However%2C%20both%20leaders%20faced%20significant%20defeats%20in%20their%20respective%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaje%2C%20a%20two-time%20chief%20minister%20and%20former%20minister%20in%20the%20A.B.%20Vajpayee%20government%2C%20was%20not%20given%20the%20opportunity%20for%20a%20third%20term.%20This%20was%20even%20though%20Raje%20campaigned%20for%2049%20candidates%2C%20of%20whom%2036%20emerged%20victorious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Chouhan%2C%20to%20assert%20her%20claim%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20chair%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20also%20went%20to%20Delhi%20and%20met%20with%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%2C%20but%20now%20it%20seems%20that%20things%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20in%20her%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Yaqut%20Ali.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%